{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"x","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/x","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>该属性在用户坐标系统中标识了一个 x 轴坐标。本坐标的确切效果依赖于每个元素。大多数时候，它体现了引用元素的矩形区域的左上角的 x 轴坐标（请阅读每个元素的文档以了解例外情况）。</p>\n\n<p>如果没有指定这个属性，效果相当于值被设置为 0，除了<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a>元素以及<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a>元素；这两个元素的<code>x</code>默认值为<strong>-10%</strong>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#coordinate\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Content_type#Coordinate\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#AltGlyphElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): altGlyph element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/interact.html#CursorElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): cursor element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#fePointLightXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): fePointLight element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#feSpotLightXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): feSpotLight element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#FilterElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): filter element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/extend.html#ForeignObjectElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): foreignObject element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#GlyphRefElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): glyphRef element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#ImageElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): image element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/pservers.html#PatternElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): pattern element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/shapes.html#RectElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): rect element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#SVGElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): svg element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#TextElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): text element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#UseElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): use element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/filters.html#FilterPrimitiveXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): Filter primitive</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/masking.html#MaskElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): mask element</a><br>\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/text.html#TSpanElementXAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition): tspan element</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p></p><dl>\n  <dt id=\"coordinate_2\">&lt;coordinate&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A &lt;coordinate&gt; is a length in the user coordinate system that is the given distance from the origin of the user coordinate system along the relevant axis (the x-axis for X coordinates, the y-axis for Y coordinates). Its syntax is the same as that for <a href=\"#length\">&lt;length&gt;</a>.</p>\n    <p>Within the SVG DOM, a &lt;coordinate&gt; is represented as an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGLength\"><code>SVGLength</code></a> or an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedLength\"><code>SVGAnimatedLength</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>x</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#filterprimitive\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#FilterPrimitive\">滤镜元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/fePointLight\"><code>&lt;fePointLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpotLight\"><code>&lt;feSpotLight&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/foreignObject\"><code>&lt;foreignObject&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/glyphRef\"><code>&lt;glyphRef&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mask\"><code>&lt;mask&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"x","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"x","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"x","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"x","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/x","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/x/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/x","title":"x"}],"pageTitle":"x - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}